May 2015: Some notes on installing on Kali 1.1.0

apt-get update
apt-get upgrade
git clone https://github.com/pentestmonkey/yaptest.git
cd yaptest
./apt-get-install-some-dependencies.sh
./yaptest-check-dependencies.sh
apt-get install libtemplate-perl
... more to follow ...

Also see: http://pentestmonkey.net/yaptest/installing/yaptest-installation
